dct_title_s: Meiji kaisei Tōkyō zenzu Map of Tokyo.
dct_description_sm: Copperplate print. In Japanese. North oriented toward upper right. Relief shown by hachures. Includes brief explanatory text, address chart, guide for tourists, time-table and legend in Japanese and English. Includes inset map of Yokohama. Views of tourist attractions in borders. 1 map: col.; 45 x 67 cm., folded in cover 18 x 11 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
